Basic Parser

Queries are designed to process, filter, and summarize data effectively.
Specifically, queries allow you to:
- Filter out irrelevant data
- Select specific components of the data to view
- Group, summarize, and calculate metrics on the data

You can construct queries progressively. Here are examples of how to build them:

